	<img src="/uploads/image/201508/212f5f76a292.jpg" width="1080" height="544" title=" " alt=" " /><img src="/uploads/image/201508/fc12a1769e9e.jpg" width="1080" height="544" title=" " alt=" " /><img src="/uploads/image/201508/13c691418028.jpg" width="1080" height="544" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<a href="http://www.elle.com.hk/fashion/style_insight/Boss-FW-collection-mix-and-match-with-Bespoke-bag-for-work-style" target="_blank">&nbsp;Boss 最新秋冬款女装</a><span style="text-align:start;">及</span><a href="http://www.elle.com.hk/fashion/news/boss-bespoke-handbags-fall-winter-2015/(offset)/8" target="_blank">手包</a><span style="text-align:start;">，</span><span>加入男装元素，适合</span>女强人职场造型。<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201508/a14144bc2023.jpg" width="885" height="590" title=" " alt=" " /><img src="/uploads/image/201508/55a320d441e0.jpg" width="885" height="532" title=" " alt=" " style="text-align:left;" />&nbsp;<a href="http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Opening-Ceremony-and-Calvin-Klein-team-up-for-underwear-line,560346.html#.VdC59XhVfBJ" target="_blank">The Opening Ceremony 和 Calvin Klein 最经典的内衣线合作推出了男女款限量内衣</a>，主要有黑白灰的男士 T 恤、短裤和女士裹胸等，保留了 CK 标志性的宽边松紧，并加上了 The Opening Ceremony 的 Logo，售价大致在 30-45 美元
</p>
